---
title: Crispy Chicken Parmigiana Salad with Potatoes and Spinach
description: Everyone knows the best part of Chicken Parmigiana is the layer of gooey cheese on top of crispy chicken. We’re recreating that same combination, but lightening it up in salad form.  We think it’s the most delicious way to get in those leafy greens!
